participant "Agent Runtime Bootstrap" as Bootstrap
participant "Runtime Assembler" as Assembler
participant "Model Manager" as ModelManager
participant "Tool Manager" as ToolManager
participant "Skill Manager" as SkillManager
participant "Managed Prompt Builder" as Prompt
database "Agent Runtime Registry" as Registry
participant "Readiness Gate" as Readiness

Container -> Bootstrap: start
Bootstrap -> Readiness: REFUSING_TRAFFIC
Bootstrap -> Registry: begin BOOTSTRAPPING
Bootstrap -> Plan: list required agent id + version
Plan --> Bootstrap: pinned agent references
Bootstrap -> ConfigRepo: get exact configurations
ConfigRepo --> Bootstrap: versioned AgentConfig set

loop each required AgentConfig
  Bootstrap -> Assembler: assemble(config)
  Assembler -> ModelManager: resolve model manifest
  ModelManager --> Assembler: pinned model descriptors
  Assembler -> ToolManager: bind raw toolsets
  ToolManager --> Assembler: pinned tool manifest
  Assembler -> SkillManager: bind raw skill refs
  SkillManager --> Assembler: pinned skill manifest
  Assembler -> Prompt: compile static system + lists
  Prompt --> Assembler: static system prompt
  Assembler --> Bootstrap: immutable runtime revision
